<br>
But dammit, I want to help SLAY the old world dragons. Just once.<br>
<br>
I'm tired of not getting healed at ALL in the fights. I'm tired of getting the beast to 50 percent then watching the entire raid drop one by one as no one knows what to do.<br>
<br>
I'm thinking it's time for me to try to organize one of these pickup raids. Maybe it'll go smoother.<br>
<br>
Probably not.<br>
<br>
But you know, not EVERYONE goes on these raids for phat old world lewtz.<br>
<br>
Some of us just want to help slay a dragon.<br>
